    "For instance, LLMs can provide students instant feedback on their coding assignments or generate diverse examples of code that help demonstrate programming concepts [35].",
    "Moreover, as Generative AIs are becoming popular in production environments, familiarizing students with these technologies is increasingly becoming a crucial aspect of computer science education.The unique challenges posed by LLMs stem from the difficulty in detecting the use of AI tools [54,58].",
